<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Item Order Request</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #888888;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            font-size: 14px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Item Order Request</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= supplierName %>,</p>
            <p>We are writing to request an order for the following item:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Item Name:</strong> <%= itemName %></li>
                <li><strong>Quantity Needed:</strong> <%= quantity %></li>
            </ul>
            <p>Please confirm the availability and expected delivery date as soon as possible.</p>
            <a href="mailto:<%= email %>" class="btn">Reply to this Request</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact our purchasing department.</p>
            <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
